<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>{% block title %}WA-RS{% endblock %}</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg-void: #0a0a0f;
            --bg-surface: #12121a;
            --bg-elevated: #1a1a24;
            --bg-hover: #22222e;
            --border-dim: #2a2a3a;
            --border-glow: #3a3a4a;
            --text-primary: #e8e8f0;
            --text-secondary: #8888a0;
            --text-dim: #555566;
            --accent-primary: #00ff9d;
            --accent-secondary: #00cc7d;
            --accent-glow: rgba(0, 255, 157, 0.15);
            --danger: #ff4757;
            --warning: #ffa502;
            --success: #00ff9d;
            --info: #6c99bb;
        }

        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

        body {
            font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
            background: var(--bg-void);
            color: var(--text-primary);
            min-height: 100vh;
            line-height: 1.6;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            background-image:
                radial-gradient(ellipse at 0% 0%, rgba(0, 255, 157, 0.03) 0%, transparent 50%),
                radial-gradient(ellipse at 100% 100%, rgba(0, 100, 255, 0.02) 0%, transparent 50%);
        }

        /* Layout */
        .shell {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 260px 1fr;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        /* Terminal Sidebar */
        .sidebar {
            background: var(--bg-surface);
            border-right: 1px solid var(--border-dim);
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            height: 100vh;
        }

        .sidebar-header {
            background: var(--bg-elevated);
            padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-dim);
        }

        .terminal-dot {
            width: 12px;
            height: 12px;
            border-radius: 50%;
        }

        .terminal-dot.red { background: #ff5f56; }
        .terminal-dot.yellow { background: #ffbd2e; }
        .terminal-dot.green { background: #27ca40; }

        .sidebar-title {
            flex: 1;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            margin-right: 44px;
        }

        .brand {
            padding: 1.25rem 1rem;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-dim);
        }

        .ascii-brand {
            font-size: 0.35rem;
            line-height: 1.1;
            color: var(--accent-primary);
            text-shadow: 0 0 10px var(--accent-glow);
            white-space: pre;
        }

        .brand-version {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            color: var(--text-dim);
            margin-top: 0.5rem;
        }

        .nav {
            padding: 0.75rem;
            flex: 1;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 0.25rem;
            overflow-y: auto;
        }

        .nav-section {
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            color: var(--text-dim);
            padding: 0.75rem 0.75rem 0.5rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        .nav-link {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.75rem;
            padding: 0.625rem 0.75rem;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            transition: all 0.15s ease;
            position: relative;
        }

        .nav-link::before {
            content: '$';
            color: var(--text-dim);
            font-size: 0.8rem;
        }

        .nav-link:hover {
            color: var(--text-primary);
            background: var(--bg-hover);
        }

        .nav-link:hover::before {
            color: var(--accent-primary);
        }

        .nav-link.active {
            color: var(--accent-primary);
            background: var(--accent-glow);
        }

        .nav-link.active::before {
            content: '>';
            color: var(--accent-primary);
        }

        .nav-spacer { flex: 1; }

        .nav-footer {
            padding: 0.75rem;
            border-top: 1px solid var(--border-dim);
        }

        .nav-footer .nav-link {
            color: var(--danger);
        }

        .nav-footer .nav-link::before {
            content: 'x';
            color: var(--danger);
        }

        /* Main Content */
        .main {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }

        .main-header {
            background: var(--bg-elevated);
            padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-dim);
        }

        .main-header-dots {
            display: flex;
            gap: 0.5rem;
        }

        .main-title {
            flex: 1;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
        }

        .main-content {
            padding: 2rem;
            flex: 1;
            max-width: 1400px;
            width: 100%;
        }

        .page-header {
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            padding-bottom: 1rem;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-dim);
        }

        .page-prompt {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .prompt-symbol {
            color: var(--accent-primary);
        }

        .prompt-path {
            color: var(--info);
        }

        .page-title {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--text-primary);
        }

        .page-subtitle {
            color: var(--text-dim);
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            margin-top: 0.25rem;
        }

        .page-subtitle::before {
            content: '# ';
            color: var(--text-dim);
        }

        /* Terminal Cards */
        .card {
            background: var(--bg-surface);
            border: 1px solid var(--border-dim);
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            transition: all 0.2s ease;
        }

        .card:hover {
            border-color: var(--border-glow);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        }

        .card-header {
            background: var(--bg-elevated);
            padding: 0.625rem 1rem;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-dim);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
        }

        .card-header-dots {
            display: flex;
            gap: 6px;
        }

        .card-header-dots span {
            width: 10px;
            height: 10px;
            border-radius: 50%;
        }

        .card-header-dots .dot-red { background: #ff5f56; }
        .card-header-dots .dot-yellow { background: #ffbd2e; }
        .card-header-dots .dot-green { background: #27ca40; }

        .card-title {
            flex: 1;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            text-align: center;
        }

        .card-body {
            padding: 1.25rem;
        }

        /* Stats Cards */
        .stat-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
            gap: 1rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .stat-card {
            background: var(--bg-surface);
            border: 1px solid var(--border-dim);
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 1.25rem;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .stat-card::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            height: 2px;
            background: var(--stat-color, var(--accent-primary));
        }

        .stat-label {
            color: var(--text-dim);
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .stat-label::before {
            content: '$ ';
            color: var(--text-dim);
        }

        .stat-value {
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--stat-color, var(--accent-primary));
            line-height: 1;
        }

        .stat-card.success { --stat-color: var(--success); }
        .stat-card.warning { --stat-color: var(--warning); }
        .stat-card.danger { --stat-color: var(--danger); }
        .stat-card.info { --stat-color: var(--info); }

        /* Buttons */
        .btn {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
            padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
            border: 1px solid transparent;
            border-radius: 6px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.15s ease;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .btn-primary {
            background: var(--accent-primary);
            color: var(--bg-void);
            border-color: var(--accent-primary);
        }

        .btn-primary::before {
            content: '>';
        }

        .btn-primary:hover {
            background: var(--accent-secondary);
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px var(--accent-glow);
            transform: translateY(-1px);
        }

        .btn-ghost {
            background: transparent;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            border-color: var(--border-dim);
        }

        .btn-ghost::before {
            content: '$';
            color: var(--text-dim);
        }

        .btn-ghost:hover {
            color: var(--text-primary);
            border-color: var(--border-glow);
            background: var(--bg-hover);
        }

        .btn-danger {
            background: rgba(255, 71, 87, 0.1);
            color: var(--danger);
            border-color: rgba(255, 71, 87, 0.3);
        }

        .btn-danger::before {
            content: 'x';
        }

        .btn-danger:hover {
            background: var(--danger);
            color: white;
        }

        .btn-sm {
            padding: 0.375rem 0.75rem;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
        }

        /* Tables */
        .table-wrap {
            overflow-x: auto;
        }

        table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
        }

        th, td {
            padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
            text-align: left;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-dim);
        }

        th {
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            color: var(--text-dim);
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        tbody tr {
            transition: background 0.15s;
        }

        tbody tr:hover {
            background: var(--bg-hover);
        }

        /* Status Badges */
        .status {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.375rem;
            padding: 0.25rem 0.5rem;
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }

        .status-dot {
            width: 6px;
            height: 6px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: currentColor;
        }

        .status.online {
            color: var(--success);
            background: rgba(0, 255, 157, 0.1);
        }

        .status.online .status-dot {
            animation: pulse 2s infinite;
        }

        .status.connecting {
            color: var(--warning);
            background: rgba(255, 165, 2, 0.1);
        }

        .status.connecting .status-dot {
            animation: blink 1s infinite;
        }

        .status.offline {
            color: var(--text-dim);
            background: rgba(85, 85, 102, 0.2);
        }

        @keyframes pulse {
            0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
            50% { opacity: 0.5; }
        }

        @keyframes blink {
            0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
            50% { opacity: 0.3; }
        }

        /* Code/ID styling */
        .code {
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            color: var(--accent-primary);
            background: rgba(0, 255, 157, 0.08);
            padding: 0.125rem 0.375rem;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }

        /* Forms */
        .form-group { margin-bottom: 1.25rem; }

        .form-label {
            display: block;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .form-label::before {
            content: '$ ';
            color: var(--accent-primary);
        }

        .form-input {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
            color: var(--text-primary);
            background: var(--bg-void);
            border: 1px solid var(--border-dim);
            border-radius: 6px;
            transition: all 0.15s;
        }

        .form-input:focus {
            outline: none;
            border-color: var(--accent-primary);
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px var(--accent-glow);
        }

        .form-input::placeholder {
            color: var(--text-dim);
        }

        .form-hint {
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            color: var(--text-dim);
            margin-top: 0.375rem;
        }

        .form-hint::before {
            content: '# ';
        }

        /* Alerts */
        .alert {
            padding: 0.875rem 1rem;
            border-radius: 6px;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
        }

        .alert-success {
            background: rgba(0, 255, 157, 0.1);
            border: 1px solid rgba(0, 255, 157, 0.2);
            color: var(--success);
        }

        .alert-success::before {
            content: '[OK]';
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .alert-danger {
            background: rgba(255, 71, 87, 0.1);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 71, 87, 0.2);
            color: var(--danger);
        }

        .alert-danger::before {
            content: '[ERROR]';
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .alert-warning {
            background: rgba(255, 165, 2, 0.1);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 165, 2, 0.2);
            color: var(--warning);
        }

        .alert-warning::before {
            content: '[WARN]';
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        /* QR Container */
        .qr-frame {
            background: white;
            padding: 1rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
            display: inline-block;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 255, 157, 0.1);
        }

        .qr-frame img {
            display: block;
            max-width: 220px;
        }

        /* Pair Code Display */
        .pair-code {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 0.5rem;
            color: var(--accent-primary);
            text-shadow: 0 0 30px var(--accent-glow);
            animation: glow 2s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
        }

        @keyframes glow {
            from { text-shadow: 0 0 20px var(--accent-glow); }
            to { text-shadow: 0 0 40px var(--accent-glow), 0 0 60px var(--accent-glow); }
        }

        /* Empty State */
        .empty-state {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 3rem 2rem;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
        }

        .empty-state-icon {
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            opacity: 0.5;
        }

        .empty-state-text::before {
            content: '# ';
            color: var(--text-dim);
        }

        /* Terminal Output */
        .terminal-output {
            background: var(--bg-void);
            border: 1px solid var(--border-dim);
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 1rem;
            margin: 1rem 0;
        }

        .terminal-line {
            display: flex;
            gap: 0.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
        }

        .terminal-line:last-child {
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }

        .terminal-prompt {
            color: var(--accent-primary);
        }

        .terminal-cmd {
            color: var(--text-primary);
        }

        .terminal-result {
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            padding-left: 1rem;
        }

        /* Grid layouts */
        .grid-2 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1.5rem; }
        .grid-3 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 1rem; }

        /* Tabs */
        .tabs {
            display: flex;
            gap: 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-dim);
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .tab {
            padding: 0.75rem 1.25rem;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            background: none;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            position: relative;
            transition: color 0.15s;
        }

        .tab::before {
            content: '$ ';
            color: var(--text-dim);
        }

        .tab:hover {
            color: var(--text-primary);
        }

        .tab.active {
            color: var(--accent-primary);
        }

        .tab.active::before {
            content: '> ';
            color: var(--accent-primary);
        }

        .tab.active::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -1px;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            height: 2px;
            background: var(--accent-primary);
        }

        .tab-content { display: none; }
        .tab-content.active { display: block; }

        /* Cursor animation */
        .cursor {
            display: inline-block;
            width: 8px;
            height: 14px;
            background: var(--accent-primary);
            animation: cursor-blink 1s step-end infinite;
            vertical-align: middle;
            margin-left: 2px;
        }

        @keyframes cursor-blink {
            0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
            50% { opacity: 0; }
        }

        /* Utility */
        .text-center { text-align: center; }
        .text-secondary { color: var(--text-secondary); }
        .text-dim { color: var(--text-dim); }
        .text-accent { color: var(--accent-primary); }
        .mt-1 { margin-top: 0.5rem; }
        .mt-2 { margin-top: 1rem; }
        .mb-2 { margin-bottom: 1rem; }
        .gap-1 { gap: 0.5rem; }
        .flex { display: flex; }
        .items-center { align-items: center; }
        .justify-between { justify-content: space-between; }

        /* Responsive */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .shell { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
            .sidebar { display: none; }
            .main-content { padding: 1.5rem; }
            .grid-2 { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
        }
    </style>
    {% block head %}{% endblock %}
</head>
<body>
    <div class="shell">
        <aside class="sidebar">
            <div class="sidebar-header">
                <div class="terminal-dot red"></div>
                <div class="terminal-dot yellow"></div>
                <div class="terminal-dot green"></div>
                <div class="sidebar-title">wa-rs@terminal</div>
            </div>
            <div class="brand">
                <pre class="ascii-brand">██╗    ██╗ █████╗       ██████╗ ███████╗
██║    ██║██╔══██╗      ██╔══██╗██╔════╝
██║ █╗ ██║███████║█████╗██████╔╝███████╗
██║███╗██║██╔══██║╚════╝██╔══██╗╚════██║
╚███╔███╔╝██║  ██║      ██║  ██║███████║
 ╚══╝╚══╝ ╚═╝  ╚═╝      ╚═╝  ╚═╝╚══════╝</pre>
                <div class="brand-version">v0.1.1 | WhatsApp Gateway</div>
            </div>
            <nav class="nav">
                <div class="nav-section">Navigation</div>
                <a href="/dashboard" class="nav-link">dashboard</a>
                <a href="/dashboard/sessions" class="nav-link">sessions</a>
                <a href="/dashboard/sessions/new" class="nav-link">new_session</a>
                <div class="nav-spacer"></div>
                <div class="nav-section">External</div>
                <a href="/swagger-ui" target="_blank" class="nav-link">api_docs</a>
                <a href="/dashboard/settings" class="nav-link">settings</a>
            </nav>
            <div class="nav-footer">
                <form method="POST" action="/dashboard/logout" style="margin: 0;">
                    <button type="submit" class="nav-link" style="width: 100%; background: none; border: none; cursor: pointer; text-align: left;">
                        logout
                    </button>
                </form>
            </div>
        </aside>

        <main class="main">
            <div class="main-header">
                <div class="main-header-dots">
                    <div class="terminal-dot red"></div>
                    <div class="terminal-dot yellow"></div>
                    <div class="terminal-dot green"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="main-title">{% block header_title %}~/wa-rs{% endblock %}</div>
                <div style="width: 44px;"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="main-content">
                {% block content %}{% endblock %}
            </div>
        </main>
    </div>

    {% block scripts %}{% endblock %}
</body>
</html>
